TEXT: •The firm’s hiring and compensation practices;
TEXT: •The firm’s system of risk management and controls; and
TEXT: •Insider trading, the potential misuse and dissemination of material nonpublic information regarding corporate and governmental developments and the effectiveness of the firm’s insider trading controls and information barriers.
